  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 !",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Hand over the details of political prisoners!",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Voice of the Voiceless organization handed over the details of Tamil political prisoners who have been detained in jails for a long time to Vigneswaran, President of the Tamil People's Alliance and Member of Parliament.",
        "Voice of the Voiceless organizations met and discussed with Member of Parliament Wigneswaran at the residence of Member of Parliament Wigneswaran in Nallur and also provided details of political prisoners.",
        "It is noteworthy that Wigneswaran supported Ranil Wickramasinghe with certain conditions including the release of political prisoners while electing the President.",
        "Member of Parliament Wigneswaran promised that he would give the details of the political prisoners to the President and press for their release when he met and discussed with President Ranil Wickramasinghe."
      ],
